State.Author: Mihail
State.Description: Cockatrices are big flying chimeras resembling a draconic rooster or chicken, created by powerfull alchemists. State.Name: Cockatrices- Mihail Monsters and Animals (MIHAIL SSE PORT)

State.Author: Mihail
State.Description: Coral Atronachs are tall, slender creatures, with bodies made entirely of living colonies of coral and sponges, and sea rock covered with barnacles, as well as marine mollusks of all kinds and seaweed. Nereids are the main summoners and body creators of the Coral Atronachs in Nirn and they employ these atronachs primarily as protectors of the seas.
State.Name: Coral Atronachs- Mihail Monsters and Animals (MIHAIL SSE PORT)

State.Author: Mihail
State.Description: Dwarven Sentinels are created simply as killing machine designed for one thing: search and destroy anyone who invade the dungeons of their masters. Strangely evil, they appear as a multi-tentacled creature, with multiple glowing red sensors, that moves effortlessly through the air, probably using an advanced internal form of electromagnetism.
State.Name: Dwarven Sentinels- Mihail Monsters and Animals (MIHAIL SSE PORT)

State.Author: Mihail and Son6Of6Tredis
State.Description: In general definition, a spectre is a ghostly entity designed to perform a particular function, of its own accord or against its will, forced by a higher power. Guardian spectres guard certain locations or people, and are commonly  embedded in tremendous elemental magical power, attached to them by those who gave them their functions.
State.Name: Guardian Spectres- Mihail Monsters and Animals (MIHAIL SSE PORT)

State.Author: Mihail
State.Description: Reptilians from the provinces of Morrowind and Black Marsh, Guars are the primary domesticated herd animal of these provinces, and are usually docile and not aggressive. Characterized by their endurance, Guars are used mostly as pack animals and beasts of burden, and mounts, by the Dunmer and the Argonian.
State.Name: Guars- Mihail Monsters and Animals (MIHAIL SSE PORT)

State.Author: Mihail
State.Description: Liches are a powerful type of undead. They are mages who prolonged their lifespan through the use of one or more types of necromancy and black magic, thus transforming themselves into powerful immortal beings, but in a decaying appearance and condition, and with the constant need to feed on souls to maintain their existence in that undead stage.
State.Name: Liches- Mihail Monsters and Animals (MIHAIL SSE PORT)

State.Author: Mihail
State.Description: Few things are more pitiful than the transformation of a soul into an insane wraith. Among these, there are those who have plunged into a deep mental abyss of sadness and despair, becoming what many know as Mourning Souls, the personification of desolation.
State.Name: Mourning Souls- Mihail Monsters and Animals (MIHAIL SSE PORT)

State.Author: andi500
State.Description: Adds more and different Mourning Souls to Skyrim

State.Author: Mihail
State.Description: The Old Gods of the Hunt, also known as Ancient Leshens, are powerfull ancient creatures from a previous Wild Hunt, that still roams through Tamriel in very small numbers. Ferocious and stunning powerfull, this wild hunt beasts are related to Hircine, and worshiped since the beginning by the Forsworn and the Bosmer as one of their Old Gods.
State.Name: Old Gods of the Hunt- Mihail Monsters and Animals (MIHAIL SSE PORT)

State.Author: Mihail
State.Description: Pigeons are gentle, plump, small-billed birds with a skin saddle (cere) between the bill and forehead, that live commonly in human settlements, eating the remains of food, specially bread and grain, left behind by the city inhabitants.
State.Name: Pigeons- Mihail Monsters and Animals (MIHAIL SSE PORT)

State.Author: Mihail
State.Description: Rotten Maidens exude immense sadness, poor helpless wraiths. People fear them,  but most of all, they feel sorry for them. They are the spirits of young women who died violent deaths right before their weddings. Driven mad with pain and anger, they wander the fields searching for their unfaithful lovers or backstabbing murderers.
State.Name: Rotten Maidens- Mihail Monsters and Animals (MIHAIL SSE PORT)

State.Author: Mihail
State.Description: Shadow Atronachs are sinister elemental golems created from the energy of the shadows. They are personifications of everything that is dark, embodied with evilness, personification of terror and despair. Born out of the abyss of the original void, these creatures are among the most terrifying constructs coming from the darkest realms of Oblivion.
State.Name: Shadow Atronachs- Mihail Monsters and Animals (MIHAIL SSE PORT)

State.Author: Mihail
State.Description: Mysterious and ancient as time, the giant Snow Whales populate the most fantastic tales of the Nordic people, since they arrived in Skyrim from Atmora. These peaceful flying cetaceans were almost extinguished by the merciless hunting of the ancient Nords, leaving only a small population nowadays.
State.Name: Snow Whales- Mihail Monsters and Animals (MIHAIL SSE PORT)

State.Author: Mihail
State.Description: All types of Vampire beasts are commonly considered lesser vampires, but this description can be deceiving, for lesser does not mean weak and stupid. True, they are primitive and bear a closer relation to animals than to humans, but when they drop on their prey from above, they can be just as dangerous as their more noble cousins
State.Name: Vampire Beasts- Mihail Monsters and Animals (MIHAIL SSE PORT)

State.Author: Mihail
State.Description: Expand the concept, importance and presence of the Vampire Lords in your game, making vampires much more relevant than ever before, and amongst the most powerfull groups lurking in skyrim's dark corners.
